{"title":"湘鄂边","authors":["石太瑞"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘鄂边\t〔苗族〕　石太瑞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进　山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进了一山又一山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命豪情满胸间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头望：云在空中跑白马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头看：水舞长袖拨琴弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山有多少岭呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水有多少源？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云跑马红军骑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水拨琴弦唱当年："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峡谷风怒号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如战士喊杀声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林野莽苍苍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳出多少英雄汉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杆缨枪一团火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命烈火到处燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃！燃！燃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峰峰岭岭喷怒焰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山外顽敌气汹汹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山内分地又分田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不畏白匪重重围，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢冲出封锁线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕风雨拦征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路高歌到延安……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登山望山呵山更宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛背新歌唱不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念幸福从何来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士怀抱青山眠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士怀抱青山眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山内山外是春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军脚印哪里寻？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步山花红烂熳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古　松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身负紧急任务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去往高山里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半路晴天突变阴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落下一场滂沱雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾漫悬崖陡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤雨浇湿衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头望见半空中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵巨松好遮雨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝叶象伞开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨干似柱立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱住古松细细瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场欢喜化惊奇："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密密枪弹洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀削几层皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪放光两行字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士写下豪壮语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为党哪怕流血多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命何惜头落地！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁个战士不留名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牺牲在这里？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨过天晴山色丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天变高呵山变低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首再望悬崖路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云染红松一杆旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年七月于湘西）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}